premise_source_doc_sentence: Daredevil is a 2003 American superhero film written and directed by Mark Steven Johnson .
The Marvel Cinematic Universe  (  MCU  )  television series are American superhero television shows based on characters that appear in publications by Marvel Comics .
Daredevil is a fictional superhero appearing in American comic books published by Marvel Comics .

After donning a yellow and dark red costume  (  later all dark red  )  , Matt seeks out revenge against his father 's killers as the superhero Daredevil , fighting against his many enemies , including Bullseye and Kingpin .

Daredevil 's origin story relates that while living in the historically gritty or crime-ridden , working class Irish-American neighborhood of Hell 's Kitchen in New York City , Matt Murdock is blinded by a radioactive substance that falls from a truck after he pushes a man to safety from the oncoming vehicle .
